  ('c25ff2ad-fb8b-517b-8546-48c39e9049db', 'commercial', 'Potterycrafts', 'Underglazes', 'P4080', 'Brown Underglaze Pencil', 'Cone 06 / Cone 6', 'Potterycrafts Brown lead free underglaze pencil. Create a variety of unique decorative designs. Great for shading, fine line drawing and identification. Can be used by itself or apply a transparent glaze to intensify colour. Method Apply the underglaze pencil to bisque ware Dust lightly with a brush to remove excess particles Sponge on first coat of clear glaze lightly in order to not smear design Let dry and brush additional coats of clear glaze Good to know: Firing temperature between 1000°C - 1250°C. Non-toxic (lead-free)– Perfect for tableware. Please follow manufacturer instructions. Care must be taken when sharpening Underglaze pencils, please do NOT use a pencil sharpener. It is best to sharpen with a knife or blade. Not suitable for high firing. Test before use.', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0865/4399/1066/files/Potterycrafts-Brown-Underglaze-Pencil.jpg?v=1763993987', null, 'Brown', 'https://potterycrafts.co.uk/products/potterycrafts-brown-underglaze-pencil'),
