  ('88532241-8f4b-55d5-9be7-6ebb235cd15f', 'commercial', 'Potterycrafts', 'Stoneware Powder Glazes', 'R4343', 'Deep Turquoise Blue Powder Glaze', 'Cone 6 / Cone 10', 'A beautiful stoneware powder glaze in deep turquoise by Potterycrafts. Temperature Range: 1250-1280°C. Non-toxic (lead-free)– Perfect for tableware. Please follow manufacturer instructions. Simple to apply for both beginners and advanced potters.', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0865/4399/1066/files/Potterycrafts-Deep-Turquoise-Blue-Powder-Glaze_1f33d33a-d17e-45aa-82e9-8e642f176f22.jpg?v=1721299054', null, 'Turquoise, Blue', 'https://potterycrafts.co.uk/products/potterycrafts-deep-turquoise-blue-powder-glaze'),
  ('3e7848ab-2e2d-5aab-a665-0195a9f0fd3c', 'commercial', 'Potterycrafts', 'On-Glaze Colours', 'P4367', 'Maroon Leadfree Powder On-Glaze', 'Cone 018 / Cone 016', 'Potterycrafts Maroon is a lead-free powder glaze. Powdered colours can be used for China painting or screen printing depending on the chosen medium. Powders should be thoroughly mixed into a medium on a glass slab with a palette knife. The approximate ratio is 2-part colours to 1 part medium. Non-toxic (lead-free)– Perfect for tableware. Please follow manufacturer instructions. Temperature Range for earthenware, tile and bone China: 780-820°C. Temperature Range for porcelain: 800-840°C.', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0865/4399/1066/files/Potterycrafts-Maroon-Leadfree-Powder-On-Glaze.jpg?v=1720793439', null, 'Maroon', 'https://potterycrafts.co.uk/products/potterycrafts-maroon-leadfree-powder-on-glaze'),
